![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/5116fb0e-e836-400e-8104-93bf378dc3f2/ep304.jpg)

If you ask the interwebs, the MCU is on its last legs. A recent article on Variety has brought all of the recent problems of the MCU to the forefront, saying it needs to right the ship quickly or end up like the Titanic. Have they got right, or has the world forgotten what it took to get here? Listen and decide for yourself!  
  
Please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us wherever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  

